Vclk (vclk 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 0.35n 0 0.37n 0.9 0.55n 0.9 0.57n 0 1.15n 0 1.17n 0.9 1.35n 0.9 1.37n 0 1.95n 0 1.97n 0.9 2.15n 0.9 2.17n 0 2.75n 0 2.77n 0.9 2.95n 0.9 2.97n 0 3.2n 0]
